Privacy - GDPR,CCPA
Federal - FedRAMP
Standards,Frameworks - NIST 800-53,ISO 27001,SOC 2

-------------------------
Competing Challenges:
-------------------------

Security:
----------
Secure Operation of web interfaces
Regular Vulnerability Testing
Rapid review and Remediation of Findings

Privacy:
--------
Protection of Personal Identifiable Information , user data
Breach notification requirements
Massive Penalties for violations

Accessibility:
---------------
Global Push to Make Data Accessible
Information Blocking penalties


